teaserContent.simpleText: Bruh these people are genius. Nick & the hair salon. That’s where he was discovered. He was singing while his Mom was getting her hair done. A lady at the salon had a kid on Broadway & gave Nick’s Mom the number to a talent agency. Joe & Cup of Joe. That’s from his photography passion, pictures he would take on his journey in life & now a series. Kevin & construction. Kevin went into construction after the band ended & has a company called JonasWerner.
